OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fbright end to the day then a dry night
OL,7,Fwith long clear spells. Becoming
OL,8,Fchilly overnight with patchy fog and
OL,9,Ffrost developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAny patchy fog will soon clear
OL,12,Fthen another dry day with long periods
OL,13,Fof sunshine. Becoming warm inland by
OL,14,Fthe afternoon but cooler near the
OL,15,Fcoast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FHigh
OL,18,Fpressure will maintain the dry and
OL,19,Fsettled weather with sunshine at
OL,20,Ftimes. Feeling quite warm inland but
OL,21,Fcooler along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
